rand-new, unnamed song today! Even as time passes, there are sights we want to hold dear forever. That’s what this song is about. Please listen!”","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event268-06-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(...Strange... It’s not an Afterglow song...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(But I know this sound.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(We’ve spent more than half our lives together as childhood friends. I know every smile, every tear, every silly moment. It’s all in the sound.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(...And yet...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Audience Member A","body":"I really like this song...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Audience Member B","body":"Me too! It’s so warm somehow...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(...I never realized how dazzling the sunset looks from here...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(Maybe Afterglow was always dazzling from the start. I didn’t need to engrave it—it's always shone bright...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"A band... Let's start a band!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event06-05-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"I love watching this sunset together, and I wanna keep treasuring that feeling for as long as I possibly can.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"evenr54-11-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"I'll start viewing life through my own lenses, then. If I can manage that, it'll be best for you, the others... and myself.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event94-06-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"She was sticking up for us! She was angry on our behalf!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event129-10-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(Everybody's sound is pushing me forward. Let's go ahead, someplace farther... Someplace hotter!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event211-06-060","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(I don't even care if I turn to ash like this!)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event211-06-061","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(...I was part of that sunset too.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(When I played and sang, they were always there beside me. So many layers of sound we shared... so much happiness I couldn’t hold alone.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(It was all because we started this band together.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Audience Member B","body":"Look—they look like they’re having so much fun playing!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"Audience Member A","body":"Let’s get closer! Excuse me, coming through!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":0,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(The sun rises and sets every day. We’ve always known how short a sunset is. But every day, we ran together under a new one.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"(Why did I forget something so obvious?)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"The sunset... it’s beautiful...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event268-06-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"That was so much fun~! I didn’t expect the crowd to get that hyped!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event268-06-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Master composer Moca-chan is thoroughly satisfied~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event268-06-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"Tsugu, Tomoe... how did it feel to be back on stage?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event268-06-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"I had so much fun! I still miss Ran-chan at the center of the stage though...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event268-06-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"But now I know how to keep our promise to her—just keep running.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"kime01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event268-06-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"And someday, I want all five of us to watch the same sunset from the stage again.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nod01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event268-06-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"...Yeah, that’s a great look on you, Tsugu.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event268-06-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"What about you, Tomoe...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event268-06-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"I... I was scared for a while. I didn’t know why... maybe because I lost my sense of direction.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event268-06-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"No more big goals—no more aiming for wins or perfect lives... I just didn’t know how to face the band anymore.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event268-06-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"But just creating a song together and playing it live... it felt simply fun.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event268-06-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"Maybe it’s okay to keep being Afterglow like this—easygoing and free.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event268-06-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"Thanks for pushing me to take that step forward, Himari.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event268-06-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"No, I should be thanking you... really, thank you so much for playing with me...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"awate01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event268-06-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"To stand on stage again... to play together again... I’m just so...!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event268-06-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"